」。 专家还表示，2021 年，当地也曾出现过小范围的蜉蝣聚集，当时也出现在有水域、有灯光的地方，但没有像这次这么大的数量。专家表示，由于蜉蝣对水体和保持生物多样性有益，不是害虫，不能进行人为的干预和防控。 （来源：大皖新闻）夜晚大桥上飞虫像下雪一样 湖南一地回应：是蜉蝣，「至少上 10 亿只」_ 视频 _ 沅水 _ 汉寿"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7da36313cd2934a8f9b2bf5c9105467a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "31 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665980635"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI28mD8PTdvMcMEAMaCTExMDI3MzU1MyCI5dS2BjAAOOwDQB1yCTY2NTk4MDYzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}